==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Kyke
<hw>Kyke</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[See 1st
<er>Kike</er>.]</ety> <def>To look steadfastly; to gaze.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <altsp>[Written also <asp>kike</asp>,
<asp>keke</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>This Nicholas sat ever gaping upright,⟦br⟧
As he had <qex>kyked</qex> on the newe moon.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

